%N A110611 Minimal value of sum(p(i)p(i+1),i=1..n), where p(n+1)=p(1), as p ranges over all permutations of {1,2,...,n}.
%H A110611 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A110611/b110611.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000</a>
%H A110611 Leonard F. Klosinski, Gerald L. Alexanderson and Loren C. Larson, <a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/2975240">The Fifty-Seventh William Lowell Putnam Competition</a>, Amer. Math. Monthly, 104, 1997, 744-754, Problem B-3.
